  <Docs>
    <summary>
      <para> is a subclass of . </para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>It knows how to render a map based of tiles. The tiles must be in a .PNG format while the map must be a .TGA file.</para>
      <para>For more information regarding the format, please see this post: <ulink url="http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/archives/27">http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/archives/27</ulink></para>
      <ulink url="http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/archives/27">http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/archives/27</ulink>
      <para>All features from <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCAtlasNode" /> are valid in <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCTileMapAtlas" /></para>
      <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCAtlasNode" />
      <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCTileMapAtlas" />
      <para>IMPORTANT: This class is deprecated. It is maintained for compatibility reasons only. You SHOULD not use this class. Instead, use the newer TMX file format: <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCTMXTiledMap" /></para>
      <see cref="T:CocosSharp.CCTMXTiledMap" />
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
